powerbot - An open source automation package for the popular MMORPG, Runescape


Dependencies
------------

Apache Ant


Compiling - Linux
-----------------

Powerbot uses a tool known as "Apache Ant" to automate the build process. Ant is
similar to make, however it is designed specifically for building java
applications. To build powerbot, simply issue the following inside the project
directory:

	$ ant

Once complete, you may launch powerbot with the provided run script:

	$ ./run
